To use:

    1) Optionally run these commands to build the firmware:
           cd tools
           make
           cd ../rom
           make
           cp zm2_rom.vhd ../fpga/

    2) Build the fpga/zm2.xise project in Xilinx ISE

    3) Upload top.bit to a Papilio Pro board

    4) Connect a VGA wing to slot CL

    5) Connect a PS2 wing to slot CH

    6) You should now have a BASIC prompt on the screen

    7) To play a game of breakout, type:
           CALL $FC00


